MISTRAL MYERS: Field trip?

00:34:54.710 --> 00:34:55.730
MICHAEL RAUCH: It's
a great club, yeah.

00:34:55.730 --> 00:34:56.300
ALAN CUMMING: It's such fun.

00:34:56.300 --> 00:34:56.630
MISTRAL MYERS: That's fantastic.

00:34:56.630 --> 00:34:58.130
ALAN CUMMING:
Actually, I think it--

00:34:58.130 --> 00:35:00.730
because I include Club
Cumming in the list of things

00:35:00.730 --> 00:35:03.044
