00:36:04.180 --> 00:36:05.460
and it's a tiny little stage.

00:36:05.460 --> 00:36:09.620
And I said, so, where are you
on the Baby Spice spectrum?

00:36:09.620 --> 00:36:13.487
And he said something mean about
the other Baby Spice person.

00:36:13.487 --> 00:36:15.070
And the audience
were a bit [GROANS]..

00:36:15.070 --> 00:36:17.386
And I went, oh, gosh,
I'm going to have to ask

00:36:17.386 --> 00:36:18.510
you to leave the stage now.

00:36:18.510 --> 00:36:19.610
And he was like, what?

00:36:19.610 --> 00:36:22.490
And I went, that did not meet
the level of kindness that

00:36:22.490 --> 00:36:25.395
is expected at Club Cumming,
and so you're disqualified

00:36:25.395 --> 00:36:26.270
from the competition.

00:36:26.270 --> 00:36:27.478
He was like, are you serious?

00:36:27.478 --> 00:36:29.120
I went, yes, please
leave the stage.

00:36:29.120 --> 00:36:30.182
And everyone cheered.

00:36:30.182 --> 00:36:31.640
And then what was
great was-- well,

00:36:31.640 --> 00:36:34.532
it wasn't great-- but he
went off stage, and fell off

00:36:34.532 --> 00:36:35.240
and cut his knee.

00:36:35.240 --> 00:36:38.060
[LAUGHTER]

00:36:38.060 --> 00:36:41.640
And so Daniel, my partner
in the bar, looked up

00:36:41.640 --> 00:36:43.570
and he went, spice karma.

00:36:43.570 --> 00:36:46.010
Then Daniel was putting
vodka on his knee.

00:36:46.010 --> 00:36:48.890
And this boy dressed as Baby
Spice was getting vodka,

00:36:48.890 --> 00:36:50.000
wasting vodka on his knee.

00:36:50.000 --> 00:36:52.100
But I just, like, that's
really important to me.

00:36:52.100 --> 00:36:53.970
I don't want that
bad energy in my bar,

00:36:53.970 --> 00:36:54.990
do you know what I mean?

00:36:54.990 --> 00:36:56.930
I'm just like, no.

00:36:56.930 --> 00:36:58.650
The staff know that, too.

00:36:58.650 --> 00:37:03.530
If I hear-- if any of us who
run it hear of people being mean

00:37:03.530 --> 00:37:05.540
to customers, or just
being mean in general--

00:37:05.540 --> 00:37:07.670
and I don't mean you
need to be like a robot.

00:37:07.670 --> 00:37:10.400
Just actually be kind, you know?

00:37:10.400 --> 00:37:12.235
So that's very important to me.

00:37:12.235 --> 00:37:14.360
MISTRAL MYERS: Last question
is, do you sleep ever?

00:37:14.360 --> 00:37:14.882
ALAN CUMMING: I do, I do.

00:37:14.882 --> 00:37:15.967
MISTRAL MYERS: Do you,
like, eat or take breaks?

00:37:15.967 --> 00:37:16.020
ALAN CUMMING: I do, actually.

00:37:16.020 --> 00:37:17.600
MISTRAL MYERS: Or no, it's
just work around the clock?

