00:37:21.389 --> 00:37:22.430
I think that's the thing.

00:37:22.430 --> 00:37:26.670
I really focus on where
I am, what I'm doing.

00:37:26.670 --> 00:37:30.674
Then I focus on fun
as well, you know.

00:37:30.674 --> 00:37:31.590
And I'm a good napper.

