ALAN CUMMING: And
then when we dance--

00:49:57.870 --> 00:49:59.970
we have this thing
where one of the--

00:49:59.970 --> 00:50:02.670
there's probably about three
cameras all going at once.

00:50:02.670 --> 00:50:03.670
And they have the dolly.

00:50:03.670 --> 00:50:05.130
You know, the thing
they'd push like that.

00:50:05.130 --> 00:50:06.960
And they have these
little, you know,

00:50:06.960 --> 00:50:09.165
like Alexa-- oh, what's
the Google version?

