MISTRAL MYERS: Google Home.

00:50:11.310 --> 00:50:12.060
ALAN CUMMING: Google Hum?

00:50:12.060 --> 00:50:13.030
MISTRAL MYERS: Google Home.

00:50:13.030 --> 00:50:14.238
ALAN CUMMING: Home, oh I see.

00:50:14.238 --> 00:50:14.890
Google Hum.

00:50:14.890 --> 00:50:17.040
Bit of a Google Hum.

