Just on the stages,
that would be our thing,

00:50:30.519 --> 00:50:31.560
we'd just be like mm-hmm.

00:50:31.560 --> 00:50:33.870
And you can tell different
directors who are coming

00:50:33.870 --> 00:50:35.220
in were like, what's going on?

